News



Perspective Magazine Discusses What's Next for the Open-Office Workspace

Perspective Magazine features Tracy Wymer, Knoll vice president of workplace research and strategy. 



Knoll at Dwell on Design 2017

Knoll celebrates 100 years of Florence Knoll and her designs at this year's Dwell on Design at the Los Angeles Convention Center. 



Knoll Design and Workplace Seminars at NeoCon 2017 

Knoll 2017 NeoCon seminars cover a range of topics from industry trends to 100 years of Florence Knoll 



Tech Talk at NeoCon 2017 

Knoll hosts panel discussion on the importance of integrating technology into today's evolving workplace. 



Knoll Showcases Immersive Planning at NeoCon 2017 

Knoll presents a range of Immersive planning solutions. Raised Anchor Storage wins Best of NeoCon Gold. 


